window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They asked for the impossible and he delivered—so why does it feel like he's being punished?</b></p> <p>When a ruthless commander takes over the moon, he has it out for Carter Ash. The commander sends him to a tiny settlement to defend it with the worst soldiers for the job. Carter’s only support comes from an unexpected place: an enticing alien diplomat.</p> <p>That’s not all, however—the meager soldiers he has are being hunted and killed by something outside the colony.</p> <p>An old enemy is back, and they’re out for blood.</p>"; 
